      • newItem

        Item newItem(java.lang.String commandInput)
        Parses a new Item with a given command input string. This String needs to be formatted like:
        itemName:data or
        itemId:data
        Alternatively it can only be the itemId or name, then default 0 will be set as data
        Parameters:
        commandInput - the string command
        Returns:
        Item or null if the itemName/id is not a valid ItemType
